Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.25,0:00:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的鼻息氣弄的我很癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.32,0:00:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.14,0:00:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為什麼還要直接連接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.46,0:00:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.41,0:00:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小拓那邊拷貝失敗了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就從你這邊安裝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.11,0:00:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.69,0:00:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛……等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.26,0:00:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你這裏就沒根像樣點的線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你自己不帶根長點的過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 最後再向你確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我待會兒就要傳送給你的Brain Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖是遊戲但又不是遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能有一天 會讓你後悔現在的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果抱著 有了就能獲得強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種輕浮的心態…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊 我不是說過很多遍了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是想要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想告訴小春和小拓你們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲是要輕輕鬆鬆玩才有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.71,0:00:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:03.00,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an5\pos(437,125)\fs20}程序下載 安全警告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:03.00,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an5\pos(428,210)\fs20}要執行BB2039嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:03.00,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(500,500)\an5\pos(296,313)}執行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:03.00,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(500,500)\an5\pos(569,313)}取消
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春 我很怕……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕小千改變…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要由我們…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能保護好她就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不一定能安裝成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W……Welcome to the……Accelerated·World？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:28.15,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(657,392)}Violation ；侵入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給豬君下達今天的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼倒現在還做這種夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒換教室該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春 還醒著沒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風刮的很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花都要被吹散了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 我把門給你打開 直接登錄到我家來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 現在去…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧 那就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 真是沒辦法的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接連接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Direct link>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是奇蝦哦 寒武紀時代的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在用那個虛擬角色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明可以隨便換一個的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經習慣這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 這個靠枕地獄…不…天國到底是咋回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧 前段時間作為升級獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增設了我的專用存儲空間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持這種解像度 從一邊到另一邊有足足十五公里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 讓我也玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓小春個性化的話 就會只有油煙 鐵屑和霧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣才好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把對戰戰車 BF109戰鬥機什麼的放在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 不要動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 幹啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你對我說今晚有可能會做噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才搞的我睡不著的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這沒辦法啊 如果不做夢的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥角色就製造不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥角色是因為心靈的創傷 而決定出來的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果心靈沒有創傷的人話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太失禮了 心靈創傷人人都有的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說小學遠足時 有哪位仁兄做巴士暈車在我大腿上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 實在對不起 請不要再說下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 別給我動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是枕頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前小春到我家過夜時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你當枕頭睡總感覺睡的很踏實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前…這都多少年前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…真的努力了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能成為超頻連接者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(490,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很努力了 所以肯定能變回去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變回大家一能起玩笑那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會誰都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 怎麼 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 怎麼了 為什麼在哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 什麼都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 三人能在一個教室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 真是太巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別一直玩網絡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早會要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位大多數
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在滿懷著期待的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也感受著相等的不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是新入學的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於新的校舍 陌生的高年級學生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定都會感到迷茫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說著這樣漂亮訓話的人 在另一個世界竟是秩序的破壞者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時又是連美國海軍部隊 都要大吃一驚的魔鬼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}但是 希望各位能去想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}現在在你們後面的那些一臉嚴肅的人們 在一年前 兩年前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是和你們一樣懷抱著不安站在相同的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}請大家後好享受接下來的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成學姐還會讀心術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:07:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時間也許看起來很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時間也許看起來很多 但其實一瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家一定要充實的利用好這一年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的講話到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著有請生活指導老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}就校內神經連接終端的使用注意事項進行說明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs18\pos(350,38)}<Neural Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生裏有超頻連接者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(478,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才學姐好像注意到什麼一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直盯著新生那邊看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般說來超頻連接者 都和為他安裝程序的父母上同一個學校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(242,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是可能性也並不是零
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之去確認一下比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生手冊也快分發完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這會兒正是新生連接上走廊局域網的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burst…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個又偷偷的不帶上我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為我不知道 你們要去加速世界對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你們幫我裝這個遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我想知道 遊戲該開開心心的玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是總不帶上我 不就沒意義了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小拓你就做下旁觀者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都要消耗一點超頻點數
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(532,430)}<Burst Point>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好看看 小千的對戰角色是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 那我要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就站在那裏就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會邀請你對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那準備開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Burst Link>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是小千的對戰角色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是 青橙鈴音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(470,430)}<Lime Bell>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青橙鈴音 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(407,430)}<Lime Bell>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得顏色有點太鮮艷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就別抱怨了 能有那麼高的色彩度可是很不容易的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你是小春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色反映了你的心靈創傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事不說也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你要說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊那個就是小拓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如你的印象 和小春就是不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春 果然新生裏沒有超頻連接者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(533,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對戰列表裏有的也就是 白銀之鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(564,430)}<Silver Crow>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之睡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Black Lotus>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色之樁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Cyan Pile>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 青橙鈴音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(455,430)}<Lime Bell>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:11:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說這些 現在我和小春處於對戰狀態對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急啊 你知道遊戲規則嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分都從小拓那聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡而言之就是痛扁敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停拿分 升到10級就通關了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總結的倒真簡單明瞭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 沒有什麼必殺技嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 真是的 畫面上不是有體力槽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那裏打開技能表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是必殺技…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檸檬召喚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Citron Call>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說你要把話聽完的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要發動必殺技必須要把蓄力槽蓄滿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己受到傷害或者給予對方傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有把周圍的目標物破壞也行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 青橙鈴音 的體力值竟然沒有下降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(315,430)}<Lime Bell>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在工廠舞台破壞東西的話應該會受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防禦力很高嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒沒什麼 蓄力槽應該滿了差不多可以發動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊真的 你早點說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再來一次 檸檬召喚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(510,430)}<Citron Call>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嗎 什麼也沒發生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不應該是這樣的 難道說是妨礙視線之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼小氣的必殺技啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春你把你的必殺技給我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真的辦不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是單純的迷惑技能的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那蓄力槽消耗的也太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻沒有傷害也沒有弱化對方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你手上那個Bell把小春打飛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正想這麼干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害還不夠 還得再來兩次左右
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多可以了 小千再一次對小春放一次必殺技
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檸檬召喚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Citron Call>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我猜的沒錯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體力槽回復了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣 青橙鈴音 是治癒師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(438,430)}<Lime Bell>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治癒師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.89,0:14:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是治癒師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 小拓也很吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是可能會引起騷動一定不要公開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓武君的決斷是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果此時公開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼東京都內的超頻連接者肯定會集中到這進行搶奪戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(354,430)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治癒師有那麼厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速世界誕生以來整整7年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只出現過兩個會回復技能的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且其中一個為了制止因為自己而發生的爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動退出了加速世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那現在除了青橙鈴音 之外 只還剩一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(390,430)}<Lime Bell>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個人現在還是六王之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六王之一 是什麼顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我連他的名字也不想讓你聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不希望你對這件事抱有任何興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我是相信你的 你不會對其他的王感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會跳槽到他們那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使如此 我的不安也難以停息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春雪君你是屬於我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止以及從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後永遠都不會把你讓給別人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像脫離主題了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之回復能力在加速世界裏不僅稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是強有力的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倉島她人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在小拓為了防止她輕舉妄動而保持警戒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來需要找個時間和她坦誠談一談了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:16:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐和小千的談話嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺會很那啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍團？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(411,430)}<Legion>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我和小春屬於黑暗星雲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(535,430)}<Nega Nebulas>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領導者是黑雪姬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這樣我們三人就能像以前那樣…一起玩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家能回到以前那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先在此告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 沖繩的特產 有什麼想要的話就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沖繩？你要去旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道？三年級學生從下週日開始就是休學旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休學旅行？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在的期間就拜託你看家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 倉島君的事情就得推到十天後了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:17:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等 那領土戰怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死守
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能忍受 在這杉並區裏豎著別的軍團的旗幟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣好了 如果下周的防衛戰你贏了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為獎勵 我讓你實現一個願望 不管是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎勵？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣了 自己想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獎勵…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃 果然食物才是王道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 不是這種
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要直接連線就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸 呼吸會接觸到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太糟糕了 我太糟糕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是回去冷靜想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你沒受傷 那麼再見 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死守吧…嗎？ 真符合我王的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,符合什麼的…你還真是冷靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須兩個人應付領土戰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有其他辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經做好應付這種事態的覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從加入黑暗星雲開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(439,430)}<Nega Nebulas>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 小千那邊怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的回復角色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不戰鬥 如果加入我們的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:19:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家能回到以前那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 不小心迷路了 小拓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才被得了一分 現在是一比一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有以前贏到底的感覺 但他也很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有用加速的力量了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓 在校內比賽拿不下第一的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對外比賽可是沒戲的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胴！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胴有效！勝負已分！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個學生 應該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決賽 紅方 能美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:19:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能美…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白方 黛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個新生到底是何方神聖 感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 小拓 打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春也來加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 聲音太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護手有效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪 明明已經繞到前面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被避開不說 還被得分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brust…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超頻連接
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs20\pos(424,430)}<Burst Link>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明確認得很詳細了 為什麼到現在為止都沒出現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他剛才確實說了Burst
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.13,0:21:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小拓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burst out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效！勝負已分！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝者 紅方 能美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:40.94,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(664,393)}Arrestation ; 策略
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.31,0:23:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}下集 Arrestation
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.61,0:23:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}踏上旅途的黑雪姬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.36,0:23:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}留守的春雪必須抓住對方策略的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------- ED ---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:15.15,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:18.85,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:22.60,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up your brain!Flashed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:25.18,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a burst of sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:31.34,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“谛め”がくれた 安楽沈滞の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:37.62,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつからだっただろう？ふいに輝き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.74,0:22:40.82,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,変わらずにいてと愿うこと-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:44.53,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,変わりゆく时に生きる仆ら-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:47.71,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の声を…言い得ぬ梦を…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:51.72,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君と繋がった空へ　响かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:55.99,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっと强く…この両手で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:59.31,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙全て振り払えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:02.58,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“今度こそは…”つぶやく今と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:05.75,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤さえも无駄にしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:09.05,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっと早く…君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:12.43,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たとえ羽が千切れようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:15.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪む世界　走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.80,0:23:18.96,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覚のその向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:24.47,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“真実”と　加速してく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:15.15,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:18.85,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:22.60,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up your brain!Flashed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:25.18,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a burst of sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:31.34,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「放棄」所帶給我的 安樂但停滯的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:37.62,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知從什麼時候開始  突然間開始變得閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.74,0:22:40.82,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈望永恆不變的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:44.53,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不斷改變地世界生存的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:47.71,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心聲…無法說出夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:51.72,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響徹著 這與你相連的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:55.99,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果更用力地…用你的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:59.31,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我揮去所有的淚水的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:02.58,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將永不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:05.75,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這些傷痕也不會讓它白費
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:09.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更快地 前往你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:12.43,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這雙翅膀被撕裂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:15.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要奔出 這扭曲的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.80,0:23:18.96,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著我所感受到的彼方前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:24.47,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我的「真實」去加速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------- ED ---------------------

